Author: nonnivagyok
Text: Weed kills my appetite too but I have really bad and disordered thoughts then. Like "I'm such a failure, my life is shit, why I am living" so that's why I'm not smoking frequently

Author: Dalos_
Text: I like weed for the help it gives me. I never get munchies and it actually kills my appetite, so I consider myself ironically lucky with this. But yeah sometimes the thoughts get really intense when smoking
